{"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"To increase the chance of placing high-priority labels on the map, you can"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provide an array of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":" locations, each paired with an offset value."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The renderer will attempt to place the label at each location, in order, before","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"moving on to the next location+offset. Use ","type":"text"},{"code":"textJustify: auto","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to choose"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"justification based on anchor position.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression","text":"NSExpression","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The length of the array must be even, and must alternate between enum and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"point entries. i.e., each anchor location must be accompanied by a point, and"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"that point defines the offset when the corresponding anchor location is used."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Positive offset values indicate right and down, while negative values indicate"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"left and up. Anchor locations may repeat, allowing the renderer to try multiple","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offsets to try and place a label using the same anchor.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When present, this property takes precedence over "},{"code":"textAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"textVariableAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"text":", and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textRadialOffset"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"json","type":"codeListing","code":["{ \"text-variable-anchor-offset\": [\"top\", [0, 4], \"left\", [3,0], \"bottom\", [1,","1]] } "]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the renderer chooses the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"top"},{"type":"text","text":" anchor, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"[0, 4]"},{"text":" will be used for","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"text":"; the text will be shifted down by 4 ems.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When the renderer chooses the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"left"},{"type":"text","text":" anchor, "},{"code":"[3, 0]","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be used for","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"textOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"; the text will be shifted right by 3 ems.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property is only applied to the style if "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" is non-"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":", and"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"symbolPlacement"},{"type":"text","text":" is set to an expression that evaluates to or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"MLNSymbolPlacementPoint","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". Otherwise, it is ignored."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can set this p